WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.443
-Stay with us, friend.
-Colonel Despard.

00:02.445 --> 00:05.678
-My name is Catherine Despard.
-Ned's wife?

00:05.680 --> 00:08.118
Will you take on his case? It may be
the rashest thing you ever do.

00:08.119 --> 00:09.718
When do we leave?

00:09.720 --> 00:13.478
Mr Ralph Hanson Of the Mosquito
Shore Mahogany Company.

00:13.480 --> 00:15.398
My daughter, Cecily.

00:15.400 --> 00:17.958
Heaven save me from upstart
Irishmen.

00:17.960 --> 00:22.358
In Honduras, I was plagued by a most
vexatious specimen.

00:22.360 --> 00:23.838
If you work for me,

00:23.840 --> 00:25.238
there must be trust.

00:25.240 --> 00:27.118
-Did you do this?
-I did not.

00:27.120 --> 00:28.318
-To my mother.
-To Elizabeth.

00:28.320 --> 00:29.598
Elizabeth!

00:29.600 --> 00:32.878
We should make arrangements for your
investiture by the King himself.

00:32.880 --> 00:35.158
I'll remind Elizabeth!
It must have slipped her mind.

00:35.160 --> 00:37.358
His Majesty's Government can always
find a covert role

00:37.360 --> 00:38.758
for a person of your...

00:38.760 --> 00:40.118
..talents.

00:40.120 --> 00:42.158
What might the Government be willing
to do in return?

00:42.160 --> 00:43.758
What do you recommend? A quiet life?

00:43.760 --> 00:45.558
My head down and my mouth shut?

00:45.560 --> 00:46.960
Where would be the fun in that?

